"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1448-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:48#[refactor] Revisit Hive-Mind Phase 7 Authentication and API Key Integration: The user has requested a revisit to Phase 7 of the Hive-Mind project located at /home/michel/Documentos/Projects/Hive-Mind. The previous implementation was deemed incorrect. The core requirement is to study how Hermes handles OAuth and API key configurations for authentication and login. This understanding should then be applied to the Hive-Mind project to implement a similar authentication flow without directly using Hermes. The system needs to replicate the process of logging in via OAuth or API key, and subsequently display available models for user selection. A thorough study and a detailed implementation plan are prerequisites for this task.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"88cnk1","at":1782088667515},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05006609,-0.00350044,-0.02197394,-0.1188397,-0.04972024,0.05505043,-0.02461251,-0.01970787,0.01064301,-0.01207746,0.02986281,-0.07729635,0.0079825,0.00272697,0.02434223,-0.01290685,0.01047869,0.00289564,-0.00179564,0.04678039,0.0265276,-0.01499402,0.04627014,-0.03449923,-0.06565848,0.05200436,-0.03579662,-0.00614937,-0.03215064,-0.1925222,0.03745532,-0.03825305,0.01357044,0.00079472,-0.03929441,-0.01755875,0.00594705,0.00941363,-0.05441852,0.01029189,0.03415935,0.00573254,-0.01454132,-0.0260003,-0.03685883,-0.01942549,-0.01934747,0.02155936,-0.04926294,-0.0572914,-0.01304307,0.02711096,0.00245453,0.02015616,0.04049053,0.06160044,0.01217749,0.06435176,0.01828197,0.07012961,0.05212386,-0.00134623,-0.18417028,0.07871412,0.0660274,0.04015671,-0.04662843,-0.06100889,0.02231816,0.04283646,-0.07633217,0.00330361,-0.01448643,0.03434508,0.06418803,0.03568899,-0.07132828,-0.02780276,0.03732148,-0.05191216,-0.06539898,0.03174554,-0.00197624,0.00165907,-0.02373945,0.01177025,0.00249527,-0.01828887,-0.00453809,-0.02359387,-0.01569197,-0.02280278,-0.0257