"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1448-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:48#[feature] LLM Council Skill Implemented: The LLM Council skill has been implemented to enhance decision-making by leveraging a structured approach involving multiple AI advisors. This skill is intended for complex questions where being wrong is costly, offering a robust method for pressure-testing ideas and decisions. The process involves independent analysis by five advisors, each with a unique thinking lens, followed by anonymous peer review and a final synthesis by a chairman. This ensures a well-rounded perspective, highlighting areas of agreement and disagreement among the advisors, and ultimately providing a more informed recommendation.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1ovwe2r","at":1782088667924},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09244308,-0.00394538,0.05154959,-0.02957255,-0.03578801,0.04371808,0.03340924,0.00592813,0.03469913,-0.07698671,0.02719337,-0.00494083,0.03071851,0.03815532,0.00121425,0.04333741,-0.04828551,0.01548154,0.04929911,0.04025518,0.05316194,-0.01288942,0.01659931,0.00291157,0.01196531,-0.01332367,-0.03027883,-0.09330183,-0.06738767,-0.21974951,0.06857888,0.00900027,0.03197379,-0.01856484,-0.06170079,-0.05525819,-0.08831128,0.0500012,-0.04304145,0.05284695,-0.00245565,-0.05658044,-0.00064256,-0.06809214,-0.01742333,-0.0471677,-0.01882101,-0.05787811,-0.05472968,-0.01861707,-0.07574362,-0.05342528,0.00555918,-0.02869521,0.04619213,0.02015978,0.01778585,0.03255209,0.05561955,0.09322795,0.05857066,0.05794288,-0.2309669,0.08720694,-0.00939638,0.03391567,-0.03683585,0.03809942,0.07142562,0.04516127,-0.01593726,-0.03661733,0.06905427,0.02648669,0.04199997,0.00244755,-0.01712692,0.00046282,0.03897158,-0.02793542,-0.00955493,0.02291063,-0.00444381,-0.08486847,-0.0022173,-0.02708773,-0.03858091,0.00170027,0.02220173,-0.00087145,0.01882024,0.02731451,-0.09023426,0.01882136,-0.01965642,-0.03475629,0.02460958,-0.0278103,-0.12196346,0.14