"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1448-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:48#[discovery] Etraider UI Architecture and Documentation Analysis: The analysis of the Etraider prototype has progressed to the UI/UX layer. The focus is on understanding the screen architecture and how complex data (likely trading performance and agent states) is organized across large pages. Reviewing the documentation alongside the code will help identify the original design intent and any features that are documented but not fully implemented, which may be valuable for porting to OpenAlice.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1y8jyod","at":1782088668044},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04825973,-0.00358933,0.0809102,-0.04142829,0.00871087,0.03367812,-0.02463918,0.0436946,-0.02746875,0.00609978,-0.02460067,-0.03431937,0.02652758,0.03898843,-0.01533651,0.01736631,-0.05796596,0.03450949,0.08165424,-0.00016007,0.07082934,-0.04609583,0.05351676,-0.03310239,-0.02861964,0.12084163,-0.05186057,-0.08915289,0.01157321,-0.23663788,0.03692527,-0.03027604,0.08041559,-0.00543709,-0.01672484,-0.0139469,-0.02563992,0.01498849,0.00580866,0.00544566,-0.02581794,-0.01053907,-0.02714516,0.0034525,-0.00316221,-0.02961042,-0.04639422,-0.04781898,-0.04758246,-0.01123241,-0.01655607,-0.04375714,0.02484091,-0.0042704,-0.00590289,0.05780569,0.0394576,0.00877854,0.03691763,0.10974488,0.03420903,0.0072765,-0.19707224,0.11764228,0.050887,0.06316593,-0.07512793,-0.02356591,0.03971978,-0.01911441,-0.03314737,0.01192602,0.04159061,-0.00321852,0.03322604,-0.02840191,0.05104831,-0.03454227,0.02843865,-0.02941656,0.00930628,0.02580832,-0.01980612,-0.00518715,0.00435673,-0.04609502,-0.02608293,0.04529394,0.04315124,0.02051233,0.02513667,0.0062398,-0.05834414,-0.00048182,-0.06424896,-0.03354012,0.01643457,0.01932896,-0.0433413,0.13941002,-0.04878036,-0.03325642,0.00973705,-0.01639712,0.06942616,-0.03037244,0.0195439,-0.04656231,-0.07123925,0.0270521,-0.03227767,0.00421923,-0.06189992,-0