"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1448-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:48#[discovery] Root Cause of Frontend 404 in Bundled Server: Detailed investigation into the \"Cannot GET /\" error revealed a specific bug in the Databricks template's ESM bundling. The bundled server's internal path resolution for static assets is broken because `__dirname` is incorrectly mapped during the build process, leading the server to look for the frontend distribution folder in a non-existent directory outside the project root.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"15twakk","at":1782088668074},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.03652751,-0.0243352,0.05136638,-0.07518921,0.08411323,-0.02048212,-0.14604938,-0.00938327,0.00986992,-0.00037045,0.09240823,-0.05384333,0.0398429,0.02454618,0.01917761,-0.00218082,-0.02503827,0.01993024,0.062875,0.01006429,0.08662295,-0.03738304,0.03478688,-0.05145665,-0.033478,0.04325023,-0.03729859,-0.06703616,-0.08664208,-0.24321795,0.0529871,-0.03772279,0.00549371,-0.03268615,0.041071,-0.02816527,-0.05874116,0.02399328,-0.0422757,0.04468421,0.04479608,0.03404649,-0.01765018,-0.01588196,-0.0143503,-0.03209707,-0.01097854,-0.04676977,0.03132129,-0.05838441,-0.06298734,-0.01556743,0.00539283,-0.00631675,0.02712892,0.1244406,0.0379882,0.0666103,0.02706635,0.06820638,0.05344076,0.02626279,-0.18860485,0.02209765,0.11731578,0.03701404,0.00717132,-0.02672432,0.02039817,0.04133584,-0.02066894,0.01203183,-0.0310135,0.06466478,0.03577549,-0.01295415,0.0234622,0.02952616,0.00307274,-0.05396266,-0.036424,-0.02124155,-0.01649497,-0.03801588,0.00607311,-0.04343123,0.00144941,0.0151257,0.08427251,0.07937145,0.01858872,-0.0865794,0.0187152,0.01032114,-0.04709692,0.01542809,0.01542731,-0.00714544,-0.04559884,0.08347147,-0.0202528,0.04922492,0.01409305,-0.00052394,0.03881551,-0.02653114,0.01870955,0.04082647,0.01090609,0.00535698,0.00899275,-0.05037951,0.06009631,-0.05690863,0.03150796,-0.08496895,-0.01542264,0.00243182,-0.06926624,-0.01175